   ACR was 33 mg/mmol (IQR 6.6-130.3 mg/mmol). Five hundred and fifty five
   participants (75.7\%) reported problems with one or more EQ-5D domains.
   When adjusted for age, gender, comorbidity, eGFR and ACR, both reported
